    "description": "游戏的参与者分为两支队伍，一支躲藏，另一支寻找。游戏开始时，躲藏的队伍会有一定的时间来藏匿，而寻找的队伍则在外等待。时间到后，门打开，另一支队伍可以开始寻找。<br><br>躲藏的队伍可以变身为各种物品，并且移动速度较快。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247670/extras/04c947e509794f2b5cee86be86fd4d72.poster.avif?t=1711738500\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247670/extras/04c947e509794f2b5cee86be86fd4d72.webm?t=1711738500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247670/extras/04c947e509794f2b5cee86be86fd4d72.mp4?t=1711738500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>为了增加变身后被发现的难度，地图上散布着各种动态物品，这些物品在每次地图重新加载时都会改变位置。<br><br>寻找的队伍移动缓慢，视野有限。他们无法看透物体，不像另一支队伍。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247670/extras/b2da4c686813c421388aadfb3c292cd0.poster.avif?t=1711738500\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247670/extras/b2da4c686813c421388aadfb3c292cd0.webm?t=1711738500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247670/extras/b2da4c686813c421388aadfb3c292cd0.mp4?t=1711738500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>他们有一个特殊的手电筒，可以帮助他们寻找其他玩家。<br><br>两支队伍都可以双跳。在橱柜里，门可以打开和关闭，允许你藏匿在里面。",
